>
> Kernel                  							Time            	CPU
> 2.4.20-pre7-rmap14a-xfs-uml-shawn12d            	318.91          	80%
> 2.4.20-pre7-rmap14a-xfs-uml-shawn12d            	324.44          	79%
>
> io halfmem:
>
> Kernel                  							Time			CPU
> 2.4.20-pre7-rmap14a-xfs-uml-shawn12d            	306.82          	87%
